| c_TINYINT | c_SMALLINT | c_MEDIUMINT | c_INT | c_BIGINT | c_FLOAT | c_DOUBLE | c_DECIMAL | c_DATE     | c_TIME   | c_YEAR | c_DATETIME          | c_TIMESTAMP         | c_CHAR | c_VARCHAR |
