|         0 |          0 |           0 |     0 |        0 |       0 |        0 |         0 | 0000-00-00 | 00:00:00 |   0000 | 0000-00-00 00:00:00 | 0000-00-00 00:00:00 |        | NULL      |
+-----------+------------+-------------+-------+----------+---------+----------+-----------+------------+----------+--------+---------------------+---------------------+--------+-----------+

